  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "BIM Coordinator",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Description</strong></u></p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Create accurate and organized BIM models.</li><li>Develop plan, elevation, section, and detail drawings from the models with adequate detail and proper annotation for tender and construction.</li><li>Develop and maintain BIM standards and procedures for sheet layout, layering, modelling processes and drawing formats.</li><li>Ability to work individually and as part of a team to meet deadlines.</li><li>Manage process of coordination, exchange of data and collaboration of BIM with project stakeholders.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma in Architecture/Engineering/ Construction, Specialist Diploma in BIM or equivalent.</li><li>Minimum 3 years similar experience as a Modeller in Main Contractor firms.</li><li>Candidate with HDB BTO project experience is preferred.</li><li>Ability to read and understand architectural and structural construction documents.</li><li>Well versed in Revit/BIM software in Archi and Structure as well as MEP.</li><li>Conversant in Singapore Construction Industry regulation</li></ul><p></p>",
